imdb.plot outline: Cooklyn is what happens when a bunch of drinking buddies are asked to make a cooking show - really an excuse to explore Brooklyn, get into trouble, and talk to normal or famous or homeless people about good food. And drink and cook. Cooklyn is a drinking show with a cooking problem. This is what happens when a bunch of drinking buddies are asked to make a cooking show.
